+  // [MoCi fp-08] Export the fingerprint-config path as env var so BoringSSL
+  // (which can't depend on //base) can read it via getenv() to derive a
+  // deterministic TLS GREASE seed per environment. Without this, TLS GREASE
+  // values vary per handshake → JA3 hash unstable. With this, JA3 hash is
